<item>
            <title>[LU-15456] deadlock in ll_new_node() when running racer</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15456</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ll_new_node() will call ll_dir_getstripe() to fetch parent default LMV if md_create() returns -EREMOTE, but it doesn&apos;t call ll_finish_md_op_data() to unlock lli_lsm_sem before ll_dir_getstripe(), which will cause deadlock because the ll_dir_getstripe() will lock lli_lsm_sem again.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
